        </p>
        <figure xml:id="fig_linescalarfield4">
          <caption>Finding area under a curve in <xref ref="ex_linescalarfield4">Example</xref>.</caption>
          <!-- \apexincludemedia{width=150pt,3Dmenu,activate=onclick,deactivate=onclick,
